Betty McDowall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_McDowall 0 Betty McDowall (1924–1993) was an Australian film and television actress. She was born in Sydney, New South Wales in 1924.Her television appearances include episodes of Z-Cars, The Saint and The Prisoner.
